call BestFitColumns. This ensures that as soon as the grid is fully loaded, the columns will adjust to fit their content.
csharp
Copy code
public MainWindow()
{
    InitializeComponent();
    gridControl.Loaded += GridControl_Loaded;
}

private void GridControl_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
{
    ((GridControl)sender).View.BestFitColumns();
}
After Data Loading:
If you're loading data asynchronously or through some other method, you might want to call BestFitColumns